  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How did you find me?",
      "zh": "你怎麼找到我的？",
      "ja": "どうやって私を見つけたの？",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, your hands are like ice.",
      "zh": "哦，你的手像冰一樣冷。",
      "ja": "ああ、あなたの手は氷のように冷たい。",
      "time": "00:00:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You have to get you out of there.",
      "zh": "你必須離開那裡。",
      "ja": "そこから出なければならない。",
      "time": "00:00:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, I want you to leave this place.",
      "zh": "不，我要你離開這個地方。",
      "ja": "いいえ、あなたにここを出てほしい。",
      "time": "00:00:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who's done this to you?",
      "zh": "是誰對你做了這些？",
      "ja": "誰があなたにこんなことをしたの？",
      "time": "00:00:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No time to explain.",
      "zh": "沒時間解釋。",
      "ja": "説明する時間がない。",
      "time": "00:00:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You must go.",
      "zh": "你必須走。",
      "ja": "行かなければならない。",
      "time": "00:00:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:00:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I won't leave you.",
      "zh": "我不會離開你。",
      "ja": "あなたを置いていかない。",
      "time": "00:00:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're doing here.",
      "zh": "你在這裡做什麼？",
      "ja": "ここで何をしているの？",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Help!",
      "zh": "救命！",
      "ja": "助けて！",
      "time": "00:00:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who's there?",
      "zh": "誰在那裡？",
      "ja": "誰だ？",
      "time": "00:00:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who are you?",
      "zh": "你是誰？",
      "ja": "あなたは誰？",
      "time": "00:00:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A master of this castle.",
      "zh": "我是這座城堡的主人。",
      "ja": "この城の主だ。",
      "time": "00:00:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I've come from my father.",
      "zh": "我來自我父親。",
      "ja": "父から来た。",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please let him out.",
      "zh": "請放他出來。",
      "ja": "彼を出してくれ。",
      "time": "00:00:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can't you see he's sick.",
      "zh": "你看不出他病了嗎？",
      "ja": "彼が病気だとわからないのか。",
      "time": "00:00:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And he shouldn't have trespassed here.",
      "zh": "他不該擅自闖入這裡。",
      "ja": "ここに無断で入るべきではなかった。",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But he could die.",
      "zh": "但他可能會死。",
      "ja": "でも彼は死ぬかもしれない。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please, I'll do anything.",
      "zh": "拜託，我什麼都願意做。",
      "ja": "お願い、何でもする。",
      "time": "00:00:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There's nothing you can do.",
      "zh": "你無能為力。",
      "ja": "君にできることはない。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's my prisoner.",
      "zh": "他是我的囚犯。",
      "ja": "彼は私の囚人だ。",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, there must be some way I can...",
      "zh": "哦，一定有辦法我可以...",
      "ja": "ああ、何とかできるはずだ...",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait.",
      "zh": "等等。",
      "ja": "待って。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Take me instead.",
      "zh": "帶走我吧。",
      "ja": "代わりに私を連れていけ。",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who you?",
      "zh": "你是誰？",
      "ja": "お前は誰だ？",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You take his place.",
      "zh": "你代替他的位置。",
      "ja": "お前が彼の代わりをするんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, no.",
      "zh": "不，不。",
      "ja": "いや、いや。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You don't know what you're doing.",
      "zh": "你不知道你在做什麼。",
      "ja": "お前は何をしているかわかっていない。",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If I did.",
      "zh": "如果我知道。",
      "ja": "もし知っていたら。",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Would you let him go?",
      "zh": "你會放他走嗎？",
      "ja": "彼を行かせるか？",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "會。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But you must promise to stay here forever.",
      "zh": "但你必須答應永遠留在這裡。",
      "ja": "でもお前はここに永遠に留まると約束しなければならない。",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come into the light.",
      "zh": "走到光明中來。",
      "ja": "光の中に来い。",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, Bill.",
      "zh": "不，Bill。",
      "ja": "いや、ビル。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I won't let you do this.",
      "zh": "我不會讓你這麼做。",
      "ja": "お前にはさせない。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You have my word.",
      "zh": "我向你保證。",
      "ja": "約束する。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Doug!",
      "zh": "Doug！",
      "ja": "ダグ！",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You see?",
      "zh": "你看到了嗎？",
      "ja": "見たか？",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dad?",
      "zh": "爸爸？",
      "ja": "お父さん？",
      "time": "00:01:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's hard to say.",
      "zh": "很難說。",
      "ja": "何とも言えない。",
      "time": "00:02:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, I can't make out a heartbeat.",
      "zh": "哦，我聽不到心跳。",
      "ja": "ああ、心臓の鼓動が聞こえない。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, look.",
      "zh": "不，看。",
      "ja": "違う、見て。",
      "time": "00:02:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's breathing.",
      "zh": "他在呼吸。",
      "ja": "彼は呼吸している。",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's so big.",
      "zh": "他好大。",
      "ja": "彼はとても大きい。",
      "time": "00:02:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm not sure.",
      "zh": "我不確定。",
      "ja": "よくわからない。",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, look.",
      "zh": "不，看。",
      "ja": "違う、見て。",
      "time": "00:02:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's breathing.",
      "zh": "他在呼吸。",
      "ja": "彼は呼吸している。",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's so beautiful.",
      "zh": "他好美。",
      "ja": "彼はとても美しい。",
      "time": "00:02:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So, uh, this is your first time in the marketplace, huh?",
      "zh": "所以，呃，這是你第一次來市場，對吧？",
      "ja": "えっと、市場は初めてだな？",
      "time": "00:02:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is it that obvious?",
      "zh": "這麼明顯嗎？",
      "ja": "そんなにバレてる？",
      "time": "00:02:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, you do kind of stand out.",
      "zh": "嗯，你確實有點突出。",
      "ja": "まあ、目立ってるけどな。",
      "time": "00:02:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I mean, you don't seem to know how dangerous that go back can be.",
      "zh": "我是說，你似乎不知道那個後巷有多危險。",
      "ja": "つまり、あの裏通りがどれほど危険か知らないようだな。",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm a fast learner.",
      "zh": "我學得很快。",
      "ja": "私は覚えが早い。",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "ふむ。",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Prepare to fight.",
      "zh": "準備戰鬥。",
      "ja": "戦う準備をしろ。",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did we die?",
      "zh": "我們死了嗎？",
      "ja": "死んだか？",
      "time": "00:02:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did we die with honor?",
      "zh": "我們光榮地死了嗎？",
      "ja": "名誉のために死んだか？",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:03:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Aim the candidates on you.",
      "zh": "把目標對準你。",
      "ja": "標的をお前に向けろ。",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Faith, come back.",
      "zh": "Faith，回來。",
      "ja": "フェイス、戻ってこい。",
      "time": "00:03:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Help!",
      "zh": "救命！",
      "ja": "助けて！",
      "time": "00:03:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on.",
      "zh": "快點。",
      "ja": "さあ。",
      "time": "00:03:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on.",
      "zh": "快點。",
      "ja": "さあ。",
      "time": "00:03:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, I hate your back.",
      "zh": "哦，我討厭你的背。",
      "ja": "ああ、お前の背中が嫌いだ。",
      "time": "00:03:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What am I doing right about now?",
      "zh": "我現在到底在做什麼？",
      "ja": "今、私は何をしているんだ？",
      "time": "00:03:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Quickly.",
      "zh": "快點。",
      "ja": "早く。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Quickly.",
      "zh": "快點。",
      "ja": "早く。",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on.",
      "zh": "快點。",
      "ja": "さあ。",
      "time": "00:04:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We got to help.",
      "zh": "我們得幫忙。",
      "ja": "助けなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You missed it.",
      "zh": "你錯過了。",
      "ja": "見逃した。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How could you miss it?",
      "zh": "你怎麼會錯過？",
      "ja": "どうして見逃したんだ？",
      "time": "00:04:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You missed it.",
      "zh": "你錯過了。",
      "ja": "見逃した。",
      "time": "00:04:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You missed it.",
      "zh": "你錯過了。",
      "ja": "見逃した。",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You missed it.",
      "zh": "你錯過了。",
      "ja": "見逃した。",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here now.",
      "zh": "現在這裡。",
      "ja": "今ここに。",
      "time": "00:04:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Don't do that.",
      "zh": "別那樣做。",
      "ja": "そんなことするな。",
      "time": "00:04:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just hold still.",
      "zh": "保持不動。",
      "ja": "じっとしていろ。",
      "time": "00:05:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That hurts.",
      "zh": "那很痛。",
      "ja": "痛い。",
      "time": "00:05:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You'd hold still.",
      "zh": "你要保持不動。",
      "ja": "じっとしていれば。",
      "time": "00:05:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It wouldn't hurt as much.",
      "zh": "就不會那麼痛了。",
      "ja": "そんなに痛くない。",
      "time": "00:05:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If you hadn't run away, this wouldn't have happened.",
      "zh": "如果你沒逃跑，就不會發生這事。",
      "ja": "逃げなければこんなことは起きなかった。",
      "time": "00:05:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If you hadn't frightened me, I wouldn't have run away.",
      "zh": "如果你沒嚇我，我不會逃跑。",
      "ja": "怖がらせなければ逃げなかった。",
      "time": "00:05:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, you shouldn't have been in the West Wing.",
      "zh": "你本不該去西翼。",
      "ja": "西の翼に行くべきじゃなかった。",
      "time": "00:05:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, you should learn to control your temper.",
      "zh": "你應該學會控制脾氣。",
      "ja": "怒りをコントロールすることを学べ。",
      "time": "00:05:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now, hold still.",
      "zh": "現在，保持不動。",
      "ja": "さあ、じっとしていろ。",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This might sting a little.",
      "zh": "這可能會有點刺痛。",
      "ja": "少しチクッとするかもしれない。",
      "time": "00:05:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "By the way, thank you for saving my life.",
      "zh": "順便說一句，謝謝你救了我。",
      "ja": "ところで、命を救ってくれてありがとう。",
      "time": "00:05:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You won't.",
      "zh": "你不會的。",
      "ja": "お前はしない。",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If you kill him, you'll have to kill me too.",
      "zh": "如果你殺了他，也得殺了我。",
      "ja": "彼を殺すなら、私も殺さなければならない。",
      "time": "00:06:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Daughter, stand back.",
      "zh": "女兒，退後。",
      "ja": "娘よ、下がれ。",
      "time": "00:06:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I won't.",
      "zh": "我不會。",
      "ja": "しない。",
      "time": "00:06:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I love him, Father.",
      "zh": "我愛他，父親。",
      "ja": "彼を愛している、父さん。",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Look around you.",
      "zh": "看看你周圍。",
      "ja": "周りを見ろ。",
      "time": "00:06:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is where the path of hatred has brought us.",
      "zh": "這是仇恨之路帶我們來的地方。",
      "ja": "憎しみの道が私たちをここに連れてきた。",
      "time": "00:06:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is the path I choose, Father.",
      "zh": "這是我選擇的路，父親。",
      "ja": "これが私の選んだ道だ、父さん。",
      "time": "00:06:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What will yours be?",
      "zh": "你的路會是什麼？",
      "ja": "お前の道は何だ？",
      "time": "00:06:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My daughter speaks with a wisdom beyond her years.",
      "zh": "我的女兒說話有超越年齡的智慧。",
      "ja": "娘は年齢を超えた知恵を持って話している。",
      "time": "00:06:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We have all come here with anger in our hearts,",
      "zh": "我們都帶著怒氣來到這裡，",
      "ja": "私たちは皆、怒りを胸にここに来た、",
      "time": "00:06:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "but she comes with courage and understanding me.",
      "zh": "但她帶著勇氣和理解來。",
      "ja": "しかし彼女は勇気と理解を持って来た。",
      "time": "00:06:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "From this day forward, there is to be more killing.",
      "zh": "從今天起，不會再有殺戮。",
      "ja": "今日から、これ以上の殺しはない。",
      "time": "00:07:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That will not start with me.",
      "zh": "這不會從我開始。",
      "ja": "それは私から始まらない。",
      "time": "00:07:05"
